Rating:5/5








6/22/2017
Jason


Excellent Laptop!!!


            I'd been looking for a replacement for my aging Mac Book Air.  I saw the Surface Laptop at the MS Store and purchased it (i7/8GB/256GB).  So far it's been excellent.  I've watched movies, played games, and installed all the software I needed.  I did need to upgrade to Win 10 Pro to install some of the apps I use, but the upgrade process took less than 5 minutes, was seamless, and free.  The performance and battery life is the best I've ever had from a Windows OR Mac laptop.  The tactile elements: keyboard, keyboard cover, touchpad/mouse, and screen touch, are fantastic and on par with Apple (Apple's touchpad/trackpad is larger, but doesn't have a touchscreen).  Sound is incredible, go to the MS store and listen for yourself.  MS knocked this one out of the park.
        

