7/9/2017
Jimmy


Best Laptop for its cost and feels great!


            I know many people have different points of view on this laptop, but its a totally different story when you actually OWN the device instead of looking at it in a storefront. The keyboard feels great and the screen is perfect with the surface pen and dial as a partner. I have been using mine for a little bit of time with no flaws in either performance or style. The only thing i will say for anyone who picks this bad boy up BEFORE the end of 2017 is. Please upgrade to Windows 10 Pro. It is free and takes only 3 minutes to do and you wont regret it. I will say this though. If you do have any worries about the Alcantara Fabric. It is really easy to clean, but i havent run into that issue yet. As a student, this device provides optimal performance for those who want light, fast, reliability from a computer as well. Check it out at your local store if you are iffy about making this purchase, but overall its a great device if you want to walk into the office and see peoples jaw drop.
        

