            MICROSOFT® CORPORATION 2012 PRODUCT AWARD NOTIFICATION LETTER.
        




AL


AliKarimceo

        asked on
        
December 17, 2012








i got an email below :
 
MICROSOFT® CORPORATION
Edinburgh Regional Office
Microsoft Edinburgh
Waverley Gate
2-4 Waterloo Place
Edinburgh EH1 3EG
United Kingdom.

2012 PRODUCT AWARD NOTIFICATION LETTER.

A Copy of Our PRODUCT AWARD NOTIFICATION LETTER is Attached for your Immediate Perusal and to Congratulate you on emerging the third (3rd) prize winner in our December 2012 End of Year Sales/Award Organized For the 2012 Microsoft Edinburgh Products.You are
 advised to contact the MICROSOFT EDINBURGH UK Payment Consultant immediately.

Congratulations from the Staffs & Members of Microsoft Board Commission.
Derrick McCourt.
Regional Director,
Microsoft Edinburgh, Scotland & Wales at Microsoft Corporation UK.
 
 
After 1 reply that email, i receive another email
 

MICROSOFT® CORPORATION
{Edinburgh Regional Office}
Microsoft Edinburgh
Waverley Gate
2-4 Waterloo Place
Edinburgh EH1 3EG
United Kingdom.
Dear:  XXXX
I hereby Confirm the receipt of your Completely filled Payment form sent to this Office
for your Immediate Payment for our End Of Year Sales/Award for 2012.Your Cheque of
£850,000, 00GBP (Eight Hundred And Fifty thousand Great British Pounds Sterling)
have been issued in your name(
 
XXXX) by our Affiliate Paying Bank and this is
expected to be sent to your address in your Country for immediate payment Via Our
Affiliate Delivery Company(
Metropolitan Parcel Export Services UK) since there is a
limited time as this year is at its peak now.
Kindly Contact (Metropolitan Parcel Export Services UK)with their details below and
arrange for your delivery to your address as its your sole responsibility now to make sure
that you receive your Payment before the stated date of expiry which was announced in
our first Notification. Your Parcel has been assigned a Ref Number :( 
2012-EYSA-MXPUK)
Please make sure you include this in your message to their Company for easy
identification of your Parcel.
(Dispatch Officer).
Metropolitan Parcels Exports Services UK.
Email: *** Email address is removed for privacy ***
Alternate Email: *** Email address is removed for privacy ***
Tel: +44 7031959461
Your Parcel contain
1. £850, 000, 00GBP (EIGHT HUNDRED AND FIFTY THOUSAND GREAT BRITISH POUNDS STERLINGS ONLY).
2. BRAND NEW HCL LILEAP L SERIES LAPTOP.
3. All Original Winning Document’s that will Support the Payment of your Cheque in your Country.
I wish you a Merry Christmas and a Prosperous New year ahead on Behalf of the Staffs &
Members of Corporations Edinburgh.
Mr. Allan Vampestein.
Foreign Payment Consultant
Microsoft Corporations Edinburgh.



19 people had this question            









        Me Too
    




    Reply




    Subscribe







Abuse history














                        Answer
                    





RG


Richard G. Harper

        replied on
        
December 17, 2012




Insider




Accomplishments









If you have to ask, you already know the answer.  Do you really think that a multinational corporation would run any kind of contest or lottery on the basis of spammed, cold emails; contacting folks at random and advising them they've won a lottery or prize
 in a contest they never entered, and that they would then require you to follow up with a courier to make delivery arrangements (and of course extort pre-payment of taxes or shipping fees or whatever) ... really?
It's a shame you replied because now they have your email and think you are a good prospect to be scammed, and they will likely hound you until your death trying to get the money they intended to extort from you. Good luck!



