Rating:5/5








7/10/2017
Qian


Best Laptop ever used


            I bought this for my wife to replace her 4 year old Macbook Air which had a faulty fan. I had a surface pro 3 and she is a Mac user for last 4 years. She is a little bit skeptical when I suggest her to switch to Windows system. However,  she loves this product! (she recommend this to her friend and she also bought one as well.) Very beautiful design with cool color (she had Burgundy), and the keyboard is one of the best. Speed is super fast, battery is good (even not as good as Microsoft claimed), and she get used to the Windows quite quickly. This is so far the most beautiful traditional laptop on the market. I think this will sell whole a lot.
        

