INTRODUCING
BRAND NEW Opti Clear HD
A more RIGID 3 mil, Low-Melt, High Quality Film
Opti Clear HD (for heavy duty ) is the newest addition to the market-leading line of Opti Clear roll laminating films. Available now in widths of 25 inches and 27 inches, and in a 3 mil thickness, USI s Opti Clear HD films are produced with a thicker base polyester film to address the needs of customers seeking finished laminates that have a more rigid appearance and feel.
Buy Now





Simply the best
Opti Clear™ Premium Roll Laminating Film is our best-selling, premium quality lamination film known for its superior clarity, crystal-clear high gloss finish, exceptional quality, aggressive bonding characteristics and USI Color Coded™ .

Precision top quality construction prevents wrinkles and always provides a perfect edge seal. Forget the foggy look of cheap mono-polymer lamination films. Opti Clear utilizes a premium polymer adhesive that won't cloud, fog, crack peel or fade. 
Learn More





ARL 2700 with fans 27" Thermal Roll Laminator Kit
If you need performance, reliability and value, then look no further. This kit features two USI best-sellers the ARL 2700 roll thermal roll laminator and USI Opti-Clear thermal laminating film. The ARL 2700 laminates items up to 27 inches wide and films up to 5 mils thick on 1 inch core, and features automatic shutoff, adjustable temperature control, adjustable speed and a 2-year warranty. In addition, the kit includes 4 rolls of OptiClear thermal roll laminating film (27 inches wide, 3 mils thick, 250 feet long).
Buy Now




INTRODUCING
New 12" and 4" HD Pouch Laminators
Need a pouch laminator that meets even your most demanding production requirements and delivers superior laminates every time? The HD 1200 is the solution. Built to USI's highest standards of quality, the HD 1200 has a 5-year warranty and laminates films up to 15 mil thick. Like every USI product, it's backed by our best-in-class customer service and lifetime technical support. Make the USI HD 1200 your choice to protect documents, make signs, create your own ID cards, and more.

Buy Now





























